<br>
You will probably need at least a small group to do Lower Guk. If someone is camping the Frenzied Ghoul, offer to help them (and make sure they know you are NOT interested in the sash), and you should get that page pretty easily.<br>
<br>
Faction isn't a big problem, just don't kill any of the quest givers. Magician epic isn't faction based like some others (i.e. shaman).<br>
<br>
